name: Wire Wrapped Faceted Pink Glass Crystal Pendant, Woven Frame
description:
This piece features a glass crystal wrapped in oxidized copper wire, and rests on an  21 inch cord (at the longest length).
The piece has been left unsealed in order to give it the antique look, and upon oxidization, it has been polished to give a stunning finish.

Upon purchase, all items in my shop are packaged with love, and shipped out within 5 business days (excluding weekends and holidays) via USPS first class mail.
